        *   S3 Finale: "With Tired Eyes, Tired Minds, Tired Souls, We Slept". Dan kills Keith (sacrifice? No, murder). Maybe not.
    *   *Candidate: Gilmore Girls.* 7 Seasons.
        *   Leads: Lorelai & Luke (eventually), Rory & Logan/Jess/Dean.
        *   S3 Finale: "Raincoats and Recipes". Emily and Richard renew vows. No roommate sacrifice.
